OL,3,CParents are campaigning to keep their
OL,4,Clocal nursery open
OL,6,FParents in the Scottish Borders are
OL,7,Fcampaigning to keep their local
OL,8,Fnursery open as fears mount over its
OL,9,Flong-term future.
OL,11,FChannelkirk Primary school, in Oxton,
OL,12,Fhas capacity to take up to 20 nursery-
OL,13,Fage children, but with their enrolment
OL,14,Fnumbers dropping, Scottish Borders
OL,15,FCouncil has placed the facility's pre-
OL,16,Fschool services under review.
OL,18,FThe council says that reviews are
OL,19,Fnormal when student numbers are low
OL,20,Fand the authority insists it is not
OL,21,Fconsidering closure.
