OL,3,CParents are campaigning to keep their
OL,4,Clocal nursery open
OL,6,FHowever, parent and campaigner Paul
OL,7,FFulton says with the closures of
OL,8,Fnurseries nearby in Westerruther and
OL,9,FFountainhall, he fears ChannelKirk
OL,10,FPrimary could be next.
OL,12,FHe said: "We found out through a
OL,13,Fmeeting with the Scottish Borders
OL,14,FCouncil that the nursery is under
OL,15,Freview for closure due to the
OL,16,Fenrolment numbers for the next year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
