OL,3,CParents are campaigning to keep their
OL,4,Clocal nursery open
OL,6,F"At that point we had five enrolments
OL,7,Ffor the nursery and were told at this
OL,8,Fmeeting that there's a potential with
OL,9,Fthose numbers, the nursery could
OL,10,Fclose. That was a shock to all the
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,F"The council told us it's an annual
OL,14,Freview that happens every year and we
OL,15,Fshouldn't be too worried about it."
OL,17,FWith 11 other nurseries believed to
OL,18,Falso be under review, he added: "We
OL,19,Fwant to put some pressure on the
OL,20,FScottish Borders Council to release
OL,21,Fthe names of the other nurseries.
