OL,3,CParents are campaigning to keep their
OL,4,Clocal nursery open
OL,6,F"The other 11 - as far as we are aware
OL,7,F- know nothing about this review. We
OL,8,Fonly found out about it by accident."
OL,10,FIn a statement, Scottish Borders
OL,11,FCouncil stated: "Inactive is a status,
OL,12,Fwhich is different from mothballing or
OL,13,Fclosure, and is a temporary status up
OL,14,Fto one year.
