OL,3,CParents are campaigning to keep their
OL,4,Clocal nursery open
OL,6,F"It involves changing the registration
OL,7,Fof a setting with the Care
OL,8,FInspectorate but retains that
OL,9,Fprovision as a registered setting
OL,10,Fmeaning it can be reinstated easily
OL,11,Fwhen numbers increase to a viable
OL,12,Flevel."
OL,14,FThe closest nursery is in Lauder,
OL,15,Fwhich is nearly five miles away from
OL,16,FOxton. Parent Annabell Haskell
OL,17,Fbelieves travelling for nursery
OL,18,Foutside of the village causes concern
OL,19,Ffor its long-term future.
