OL,3,CParents are campaigning to keep their
OL,4,Clocal nursery open
OL,6,FShe said: "If we're not attracting
OL,7,Fyoung families into the village, we
OL,8,Fwould end up with an aging population.
OL,9,FIt wouldn't be as vibrant and thriving
OL,10,Fas a place as we know and want it to
OL,11,Fbe.
OL,13,F"A nursery being made inactive is
OL,14,Fessentially a shortcut to closing it.
OL,15,FNext year looks like a low year, but
OL,16,Fwe know the numbers in the next few
OL,17,Fyears will pick up, so it feels very
OL,18,Fdisruptive to be potentially closing
OL,19,Fthis nursery for one year, to then
OL,20,Freopen it.
